(Labo 1 - Thermal demand characterization) Tj
0 -14 Td
(The heating and ECS demand is derived from SIA 380/1 tables, the building SRE) Tj
0 -14 Td
(and envelope factors. An hourly profile is built with the MeteoSuisse temperature) Tj
0 -14 Td
(series and a simplified ECS schedule \(08:00-20:00\). Thermal inertia and) Tj
0 -14 Td
(foisonnement factors are applied to approximate diversity between buildings.) Tj
