(Labo 3 - District heating network optimization \(focus\)) Tj
0 -14 Td
(The optimization uses the road network as the backbone and connects buildings) Tj
0 -14 Td
(and resources to the nearest street edge. Each pipe segment is assigned a) Tj
0 -14 Td
(diameter from a discrete catalogue and sized to carry the required mass flow) Tj
0 -14 Td
(at Delta T = 30C. The objective is to minimize a linearized CAPEX function) Tj
0 -14 Td
(based on diameter and length. The heat demand is taken from the Labo 1) Tj
0 -14 Td
(peak power \(after foisonnement\).) Tj
